<br>
Personally I liked that I could solo mobs while waiting for a spot in a group to open up. Waiting while doing little to nothing is very frustrating. But if I am able to earn some xp while I wait, its much more tolerable.<br>
<br>
Maybe it'll be better when I have more of my level 61/62 spells, but from what I've read, I won't hold my breath.<br>
